{"tid":699694,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"你不再屬於你的名字","createTime":"2018-06-12T17:42:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-13T07:48:37.000Z","uid":36402,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2cef5cac158712441e41b5e9c1abf22e2535fb13","tid":699694,"uid":36402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T17:42:36.000Z","msg":"你不再被稱為你的名字<br />\n我在每日每夜都想念的你<br />\n如果你不再是那名字<br />\n是不是會隨著你可愛的名字一樣<br />\n不再代表你地消散在我記憶中<br />\n那麼整夜想的就只你對我說過的話<br />\n挽過的手，笑過的臉<br />\n親愛的你"},{"pid":"02832cf7229addffc923e965b30f3a43830e095e","tid":699694,"uid":37348,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T17:43:47.000Z","msg":"別這樣"},{"pid":"5c20544f4a9586014c2af6d2a900e30083237b08","tid":699694,"uid":165024,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T17:43:49.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"92d79b34b7f06984fa7423b75592df2d76302aaa","tid":699694,"uid":97630,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T18:16:54.000Z","msg":"掛住你"},{"pid":"0441ca729774e856299ab43d2df02a1933f068e3","tid":699694,"uid":75573,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T18:17:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"387f7f53a16a115938be7cbd1b2447594249b351","tid":699694,"uid":36402,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T01:12:58.000Z","msg":"其實可以放下，但不想放下"},{"pid":"6c3487513f083c5b12c618b4ab6ede00d755dfc4","tid":699694,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T02:28:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd1b69ff6e2a7ed372d8a924c364bd25a767232b","tid":699694,"uid":36402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T02:48:36.000Z","msg":"只係想同你做番朋友<br />\n我可以有個關心你既身份<br />\n你亦有不避諱我的理由"},{"pid":"f59b6918080bbb56fb1863112b5029af6860df7a","tid":699694,"uid":36402